A4.text: Tet symbolizes the start of the spring season.

A5.text: Tết Nguyên Đán is considered the first festival of the new year, beginning at midnight with the Trừ tịch ceremony.

A6.text: Tet Nguyen Dan: The Vietnamese New Year
